<h2>Principal Building – Minimum Setbacks (Feet)</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Zone</th><th>Front</th><th>Side</th><th>Rear</th></tr>
<tr><td>R-1</td><td>20</td><td>8</td><td>20</td></tr>
<tr><td>R-2</td><td>20</td><td>8</td><td>20</td></tr>
