<div class="card">
<h2>Accessory Buildings & Structures</h2>
<p>Accessory buildings and structures (except fences) require
<strong>5 feet minimum side and rear setbacks</strong>.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Front Setback Notes</h2>
<ul>
<li>Secondary front yard setback: <strong>15 feet</strong></li>
<li>Cul-de-sac lots may reduce lot width at building line by <strong>25 feet</strong></li>
</ul>
</div>

